source: crates/biome_formatter_test/src/snapshot_builder.rs
info: scss/at-rule/media-interpolation.scss
---

# Input

```scss
@media (#{$feature}) {.box {color:red;}}

@media (#{$feature}: #{$value}) {.box {color:red;}}

@media (#{$min} <= width <= #{$max}) {.box {color:red;}}

@media #{$query} {.box {color:red;}}

@media #{$query}, screen {.box {color:red;}}

@container (#{$feature}: #{$value}) {.box {color:red;}}

```


# Formatted

```scss
@media (#{$feature}) {
	.box {
		color: red;
	}
}

@media (#{$feature}: #{$value}) {
	.box {
		color: red;
	}
}

@media (#{$min} <= width <= #{$max}) {
	.box {
		color: red;
	}
}

@media #{$query} {
	.box {
		color: red;
	}
}

@media #{$query}, screen {
	.box {
		color: red;
	}
}

@container (#{$feature}: #{$value}) {
	.box {
		color: red;
	}
}

```
